trans-unit.source: Provides data for the **NavigationFailed** event.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o **NavigationFailed** eventos.

trans-unit.source: These event arguments contain information about a navigation that failed, and are passed to handlers of the **NavigationFailed** event, which is implemented by the following: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> NavigationFailedEventArgs encapsulates the following details of the failed navigation request: - **Navigation Initiation**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Navigator%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Esses argumentos de eventos contêm informações sobre uma navegação que falharam e é passada para manipuladores do **NavigationFailed** evento, que é implementado pelos seguintes motivos:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>NavigationFailedEventArgs encapsula os seguintes detalhes da solicitação falha na navegação:- **iniciação de navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Navigator%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Navigator%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Exception**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Exception%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Handled%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navegação exceção**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Exception%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Handled%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Handled%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Exception%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Content**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Uri%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Conteúdo de navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Uri%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Uri%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Details**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebResponse%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Detalhes da navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebResponse%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebResponse%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation State**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Estado da navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Exception> that was raised as the result of a failed navigation.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref:System.Exception>que foi gerado como resultado de uma falha na navegação.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Exception> will be either a <xref:System.Net.WebException> or an <xref:System.IO.IOException>
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Exception>será um <xref:System.Net.WebException>ou um <xref:System.IO.IOException></xref:System.IO.IOException> </xref:System.Net.WebException></xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception> that was raised as the result of a failed navigation.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Exception>que foi gerado como resultado de uma falha na navegação.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: Gets the optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation commenced.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os dados opcionais <xref:System.Object>que foi passado ao navegação foi iniciada.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: ExtraData can be used to pass context-specific data that is specific to a particular navigation.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData pode ser usado para passar dados de contexto específico que são específicos para uma navegação em particular.

trans-unit.source: ExtraData contains a reference to the object that is passed as the second argument when calling either <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData contém uma referência ao objeto que é passado como o segundo argumento ao chamar <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>ou <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, ele será `null`.

trans-unit.source: The optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation commenced.
trans-unit.target: Os dados opcionais <xref:System.Object>que foi passado ao navegação foi iniciada.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether the failed navigation exception has been handled.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define se a exceção de navegação com falha foi tratada.

trans-unit.source: When you handle <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed> to process an exception that is thrown as a result of a failed navigation, and you don't want [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to continue processing the exception, you should set the Handled property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Quando você processa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>para processar uma exceção que é lançada como resultado da navegação uma falha e você não quiser [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para continuar o processamento de exceção, você deve definir a propriedade Handled `true`.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the exception is handled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> (default).
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se a exceção é manipulada; Caso contrário, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> (padrão).

trans-unit.source: The navigator that raised this event.
trans-unit.target: O navegador que gerou esse evento.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that is the navigator that raised this event
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Object>que é o navegador que disparou este evento</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that could not be navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] para o conteúdo que não pode ser acessado para.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Uri> for the content that could not be navigated to.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Uri>para o conteúdo que pode não ser navegado.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: Gets the web request that was used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a solicitação da web que foi usada para solicitar o conteúdo especificado.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> is an abstract base class that encapsulates a web request, and is protocol agnostic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>é uma classe base abstrata que encapsula uma solicitação da web, e é independente de protocolo.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For each common protocol, the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] includes a class that derives from <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> and extends it with protocol-specific state and behavior, including: - <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `pack://` scheme to request application data files (see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: Para cada protocolo comum, o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] inclui uma classe que deriva de <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>e estende com estado específico de protocolo e o comportamento, incluindo:- <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que usam o `pack://` esquema para solicitar os arquivos de dados do aplicativo (consulte [recursos de aplicativo do WPF, conteúdo e arquivos de dados](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `http://` scheme to request files from Web servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que usam o `http://` esquema para arquivos de solicitação de servidores Web.</xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `ftp://` scheme to request files from FTP servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que usam o `ftp://` esquema para arquivos de solicitação de servidores FTP.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que usam o `file://` esquema solicitar arquivos locais.</xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> object that was used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> objeto que foi usado para solicitar o conteúdo especificado.

trans-unit.source: If navigating to an object, WebRequest is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Se navegar para um objeto, WebRequest é <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the web response that was returned after attempting to download the requested the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a resposta da web que foi retornada após a tentativa de baixar a solicitação de conteúdo especificado.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> is an abstract base class that encapsulates a web response, and is protocol agnostic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>é uma classe base abstrata que encapsula uma resposta da web, e é independente de protocolo.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For each common protocol, the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] includes a class that derives from <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> and extends it with protocol-specific state, including: - <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `pack://` scheme to request application data files (see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: Para cada protocolo comum, o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] inclui uma classe que deriva de <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>e estende com estado de protocolo específico, incluindo:- <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que usam o `pack://` esquema para solicitar os arquivos de dados do aplicativo (consulte [recursos de aplicativo do WPF, conteúdo e arquivos de dados](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse> </xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `http://` scheme to request files from Web servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que usam o `http://` esquema para arquivos de solicitação de servidores Web.</xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `ftp://` scheme to request files from FTP servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que usam o `ftp://` esquema para arquivos de solicitação de servidores FTP.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que usam o `file://` esquema solicitar arquivos locais.</xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> that was returned after attempting to download the requested the specified content.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> que foi retornado após a tentativa de baixar a solicitação de conteúdo especificado.

trans-unit.source: If the navigation failed, WebResponse is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Se a navegação falhou, WebResponse é <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.
